    "name": "Survival Quiz CITY おまつり編",
    "steam_appid": 2328530,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/a21be58f7b6b6c5a79d0f0982f19ffdb.avif?t=1770121530\" width=600 height=194 /></span>「Survival Quiz CITY おまつり編」は、多人数でクイズに挑戦し、問題に正解した「勝ち組」と不正解者となった「負け組」に分かれてチーム戦を行い、ラウンドを勝ち抜きつつ最後まで生き残って優勝者になることを目指す、<strong>サバイバルクイズアクションゲーム</strong>だ！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ゲームの流れ</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/3dface6f5442d25463092530cdb75aac.webp?t=1770121530\" width=600 height=5 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/1c4bf54c25a816cc9f127fd08a6ec7e1.webp?t=1770121530\" width=32 height=32 /></span> まずは、みんなでクイズに挑戦勝ち組と負け組に振り分けられる。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/2ffa69aeb7fcf5d3e49149d3a972e533.poster.avif?t=1770121530\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/2ffa69aeb7fcf5d3e49149d3a972e533.webm?t=1770121530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/2ffa69aeb7fcf5d3e49149d3a972e533.mp4?t=1770121530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/1c4bf54c25a816cc9f127fd08a6ec7e1.webp?t=1770121530\" width=32 height=32 /></span> クイズに答えた後は、勝ち組と負け組に分かれてバトル！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >勝ち組は、負け組を脱落させるべく、様々な武器を使って不正解者のクリアを阻止するのじゃ！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/720ec78c314b76ff04b02179a782b45d.poster.avif?t=1770121530\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/720ec78c314b76ff04b02179a782b45d.webm?t=1770121530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/720ec78c314b76ff04b02179a782b45d.mp4?t=1770121530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >負け組は、地獄のアクションステージの先にあるゴールを目指せ！制限時間内にゴールにたどり着ければ、次ステージに進めるぞ！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/5daa49032005434621b872be0f45c327.poster.avif?t=1770121530\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/5daa49032005434621b872be0f45c327.webm?t=1770121530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/5daa49032005434621b872be0f45c327.mp4?t=1770121530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/1c4bf54c25a816cc9f127fd08a6ec7e1.webp?t=1770121530\" width=32 height=32 /></span> ショップでパワーアップ</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ラウンドの合間に、ショップで買い物。アクションステージで稼いだお金を使って、キャラクターをパワーアップ！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/fe837360812902f5287fea73d0203476.poster.avif?t=1770121530\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/fe837360812902f5287fea73d0203476.webm?t=1770121530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/fe837360812902f5287fea73d0203476.mp4?t=1770121530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/1c4bf54c25a816cc9f127fd08a6ec7e1.webp?t=1770121530\" width=32 height=32 /></span> 最後の1人を目指せ！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ラウンドごとにクイズで勝ち組と負け組が何度も入れ替わり、プレイヤーが脱落していく中で最後の１人を目指そう！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/f1d7b0a008cafaf37d421994581fe4a1.poster.avif?t=1770121530\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/f1d7b0a008cafaf37d421994581fe4a1.webm?t=1770121530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/f1d7b0a008cafaf37d421994581fe4a1.mp4?t=1770121530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ゲームのポイント</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/3dface6f5442d25463092530cdb75aac.webp?t=1770121530\" width=600 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/1c4bf54c25a816cc9f127fd08a6ec7e1.webp?t=1770121530\" width=32 height=32 /></span> ゲームルールは２種類</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最後に生き残った1人が優勝する「サバイバルルール」と、最終ラウンド終了時に最もコインを持っていたプレイヤーが優勝となる「賞金稼ぎルール」の2種類が楽しめます！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/1c4bf54c25a816cc9f127fd08a6ec7e1.webp?t=1770121530\" width=32 height=32 /></span> カスタムマッチ</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >カスタムマッチで、好みのルールやオリジナルクイズを設定して遊ぼう！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/1c4bf54c25a816cc9f127fd08a6ec7e1.webp?t=1770121530\" width=32 height=32 /></span> オリジナルクイズ</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >クイズを作って、カスタムマッチで遊ぼう！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他のプレイヤーが作成したクイズも使用できるぞ。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/1c4bf54c25a816cc9f127fd08a6ec7e1.webp?t=1770121530\" width=32 height=32 /></span> ギャーくんをカスタマイズして遊ぼう！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ゲームを遊んだごほうびに、様々なエモートが手に入るぞ。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >アイテムを購入できるおしゃれブティックも要チェック</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/e13692b9406c3420adac653968148e6b.poster.avif?t=1770121530\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/e13692b9406c3420adac653968148e6b.webm?t=1770121530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/e13692b9406c3420adac653968148e6b.mp4?t=1770121530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/67a2d9ed8451ac77adbeb77a898330f4.poster.avif?t=1770121530\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/67a2d9ed8451ac77adbeb77a898330f4.webm?t=1770121530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328530/extras/67a2d9ed8451ac77adbeb77a898330f4.mp4?t=1770121530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
